<node CREATED="1463931549834" ID="ID_1463650050" MODIFIED="1463931559503" TEXT="After you choose the class you would &#xa;like your new class to derive from, the &#xa;wizard sets up the necessary header &#xa;file and source file."/>
<node CREATED="1463931631258" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_674767097" MODIFIED="1467367525096" TEXT="If this is the first code you have added to &#xa;the project, the project is converted to a &#xa;code project, which ">
