<node CREATED="1464101764626" ID="ID_570731544" MODIFIED="1464101768788" TEXT="Special constructor used internally to statically&#xa; cast one shared pointer type to another. "/>
<node CREATED="1464101775483" ID="ID_1628856446" MODIFIED="1464101776539" TEXT=" never call this constructor directly. "/>
<node CREATED="1464101782661" ID="ID_956690669" MODIFIED="1464101783008" TEXT="Instead, use the StaticCastSharedPtr() function."/>
