</node>
<node CREATED="1464339937468" ID="ID_1382377113" MODIFIED="1464340031899" TEXT="The purpose of this template is to &#xa;ensure no typos when mallocing&#xa; types that are related and will &#xa;pass static cast, but if there&apos;s a &#xa;typo could be allocating insufficient &#xa;amount of space&#xa;&#xa;//the name is VStruct because I was mallocing USTRUCTS&#xa; &#xa;template &lt;typename DataType&gt;&#xa;FORCEINLINE DataType* VStructMalloc()&#xa;{&#xa;&#x9;return&#x9;static_cast&lt;DataType*&gt;(FMemory::Malloc(sizeof(DataType)));&#xa;}"/>
</node>
</node>
<node CREATED="1464339357737" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_449523927" LINK="https://wiki.unrealengine.com/Garbage_Collection_%26_Dynamic_Memory_Allocation#Example_Usage" MODIFIED="1464340077974" TEXT="Example Usage">
