<node CREATED="1464874315883" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1235562680" MODIFIED="1464874394657" TEXT="his tutorial enables you to have a custom &#xa;event like TheSunReachedHighNoon,  have &#xa;a bunch of actors respond to this event differently,&#xa;each with their own implementation of the event">
