<node CREATED="1464874385044" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1924738020" MODIFIED="1464874473470" TEXT="d you can trigger the event via a blueprintcallable&#xa; function used in a static blueprint library">
<node CREATED="1464874435678" ID="ID_1732921890" MODIFIED="1464874463881" TEXT="This means you can trigger global actor events &#xa;from your level blueprint and ask actors to do &#xa;specific things, without having to iterate over the&#xa; actors in the level blueprint itself."/>
